quran[26]{c,v,t}:
  35,15,"Yemwe bantu! Muri abakene imbere ya Allah. Ariko Allah niwe Uwihagije, Ushimwa cyane"
  35,16,Abishatse yabakuraho maze akazana ibindi biremwa bishya (bimwumvira kubarusha)
  35,17,Kandi ibyo kuri Allah ntibigoye
  35,18,"Nta we uzikorera umutwaro w’undi, kandi nihagira utabaza aremerewe n’ibyaha agira ngo yakirwe uwo mutwaro, nta na kimwe azakirwaho kabone n’iyo yatabaza abo bafitanye isano ya hafi. Mu by’ukuri (yewe Muhamadi), uburira abatinya Nyagasani wabo batamubona ndetse bakanahozaho iswala. N’uwiyejeje (yitandukanya n’ibyaha byose), mu by’ukuri aba yiyejeje ku bwe. Kandi kwa Allah ni ho byose bizasubira"
  35,19,Kandi impumyi (udasobanukiwe amategeko y’idini) ntishobora kumera nk’ubona (uri mu nzira itunganye)
  35,20,Nta n’ubwo umwijima (ubuyobe) ushobora kumera nk’urumuri (ukuyoboka)
  35,21,Ndetse n’ikibunda ntigishobora kumera nk’ubushyuhe
  35,22,"Nta n’ubwo abazima (abemeramana) bamera nk’abapfu (abahakanyi). Mu by’ukuri Allah aha kumva (ukuri) uwo ashaka, ariko (wowe Muhamadi) ntushobora kumvisha abari mu mva"
  35,23,Ahubwo wowe uri umuburizi gusa
  35,24,Mu by’ukuri twakohereje tuguhaye ukuri (Isilamu); utanga inkuru nziza (ku bemeramana) unaburira (abahakanyi). Kandi nta muryango (Umat) wabayeho utaragezweho n’Umuburizi
  35,25,"Kandi nibaguhinyura (uzamenye ko) rwose n’ababayeho mbere yabo bahinyuye. Intumwa zabo zabazaniye ibitangaza bigaragara, inyandiko (zikubiyemo ubutumwa) ndetse n’ibitabo bitanga urumuri (ariko barabihinyura)"
  35,26,Hanyuma mfata ba bandi bahakanye (ndabahana). Mbega uko ibihano byanjye byari bikaze
  35,27,"Ese ntubona ko Allah yamanuye amazi mu kirere, tukayameresha imbuto z’amabara atandukanye? (Twanashyize) mu misozi ibiharabuge by’amabara yera n’atukura, bifite amabara atandukanye, ndetse (n’indi misozi) yirabura cyane"
  35,28,"Ni nk’uko (twaremye) abantu, inyamaswa n’amatungo mu mabara atandukanye. Mu by’ukuri abatinyamana (nyabyo) mu bagaragu be ni abamenyi. Rwose Allah ni Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Ubabarira ibyaha"
  35,29,"Mu by’ukuri ba bandi basoma igitabo cya Allah (Qur’an), bagahozaho iswala, bakanatanga (amaturo) mu ibanga ndetse no ku mugaragaro mu byo twabafunguriye, bizeye ubucuruzi butazahomba"
  35,30,"Kugira ngo azabagororere ingororano zabo zuzuye kandi anabongerere mu ngabire ze. Mu by’ukuri ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Ushima bihebuje (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be)"
  35,31,"Kandi (yewe Muhamadi) ibyo twaguhishuriye mu gitabo (Qur’an) ni ko kuri gushimangira ibyahishuwe mbere yabyo. Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umumenyi wa byose, Ubona bihebuje abagaragu be"
  35,32,"Maze duha umurage w’igitabo abo twatoranyije mu bagaragu bacu. Muri bo hari abihemukiye (bagira ibibi bakora), abandi baba hagati (bakora ibibagomba gusa), naho abandi baza imbere mu gukora ibyiza (binyuranye) ku bushake bwa Allah. Izo ni ingabire zihambaye"
  35,33,"Bazinjira mu busitani buhoraho (Ijuru rya Edeni), maze bazambikirwemo ibikomo bya zahabu n’amasaro arabagirana, ndetse n’imyambaro yabo izaba ari ihariri (ikoze mu budodo bw’amagweja)"
  35,34,"Bazanavuga bati “Ishimwe n’ikuzo byuzuye ni ibya Allah, We watumaze agahinda. Rwose Nyagasani wacu ni Ubabarira ibyaha, Ushima (ibikorwa by’abagaragu be).”"
  35,35,"We, ku bw’ingabire ze wadutuje mu nzu izahoraho, aho tutazagerwaho n’umuruho ndetse n’umunaniro"
  35,36,"Naho ba bandi bahakanye, bazahanishwa umuriro wa Jahanamu. Ntabwo uzabica ngo bapfe ndetse nta n’ubwo bazoroherezwa ibihano byawo. Uko ni ko duhemba buri muhakanyi uhambaye"
  35,37,Bazanawuborogeramo (bagira bati) “Nyagasani wacu! Dukuremo dukore ibikorwa byiza tutajyaga dukora.” (Allah azabasubiza) ati “Ese ntitwabahaye kubaho igihe kirekire kugira ngo utekereza abashe gutekereza? Ndetse n'umuburizi yabagezeho. Ngaho nimwumve (ibihano). Inkozi z’ibibi ntizizagira umutabazi.”
  35,38,Mu by’ukuri Allah ni Umumenyi w’ibitagaragara byo mu birere no mu isi. Rwose ni We Mumenyi uhebuje w’ibiri mu bituza (by’abantu)
  35,39,"Ni We wabagize abasigire ku isi. Bityo uzahakana, ubuhakanyi bwe buzamugiraho ingaruka. Kandi ubuhakanyi nta kindi bwongerera abahakanyi imbere ya Nyagasani wabo usibye ikimwaro (ipfunwe); ndetse nta n’ikindi bubongerera usibye igihombo"
  35,40,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ese ntimubona ibigirwamana byanyu mugaragira bitari Allah? Nimunyereke icyo byaremye ku isi. Ese byaba byaragize uruhare mu iremwa ry’ibirere, ahubwo se twaba twarabahaye igitabo bakaba ari cyo bakomoramo ibimenyetso bigaragara bagenderaho? (Oya!) Ahubwo ibyo ababangikanyamana bamwe basezeranya abandi ni ibinyoma.”"